cz.melkamar.andruian.viewlink.data

Class Factory<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.melkamar.andruian.viewlink.data.Factory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the objects that will be created by the factory.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DataDefHelperProvider, NetHelperProvider, PlaceFetcherProvider

    public abstract class Factory<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic class representing a factory of objects. A factory has a default instance which it returns after it is created, but this instance can be replaced through setInstance(Object).
